c=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"447225ec6fa8af525fdfa1ba154481a43c41f7a3","tid":2326030,"uid":42710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfcc0cea8d993ffb74e546e7d711d5f3ab3d5694","tid":2326030,"uid":54516,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T04:42:52.000Z","msg":"邊個專家？？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/42130\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F42130&d=ZAqn3h4t0e4XfOyVRCtvGN5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=d17b3672\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F42130&h=cf010cf5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/42130</a><br />\n<br />\n政府購三款疫苗僅科興未完成三期研究 藥劑師指缺重要臨床數據、難評疫苗效用<br />\n2020/12/14 14:01<br />\n<br />\n我們問過多個委員，大部分稱沒有選擇滅活疫苗，即科興那種技術，因當時沒太多臨床數據；亦有委員指即使選擇、都建議買少些，最終買哪一款由政府決定。有委員相信政府除了看科學數據，還會考慮藥廠是否供貨到香港、何時有和數量等。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T05:29:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5b6e02d02658071820aab455b1c4a9ed0f73e1d","tid":2326030,"uid":271807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T05:35:34.000Z","msg":"有無記者問，點解咁多國內人專程黎香港打西方疫苗，奶粉都去世界各地瘋狂購買"}]}